-google-opens-china-ai-centre.html|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171214075818/https://www.cnbc.com/2017/12/13/alphabets-google-opens-china-ai-centre.html|archivedate=2017-12-14|deadurl=no|title=Google is blocked in China, but that's not stopping it from opening an A.I. center there|website=CNBC|date=2017-12-13|accessdate=2017-12-14|language=en}}</ref>。

