2018年7月，Google推出首款[[微信小程序|微信小程序]]“[[猜画小歌|猜画小歌]]”<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/info/2018-07/20/c_137336802.htm|title=“猜画小歌”为啥能刷屏？|website=新华网|publisher=北京晨报|date=2018-07-20|accessdate=2018-08-06|language=zh-hans|dead-url=yes|archive-date=2018-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180806034731/http://www.xinhuanet.com/info/2018-07/20/c_137336802.htm}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Google takes another step into Chinese market with AI drawing game on WeChat|language=en|url=https://www.scmp.com/tech/china-tech/article/2155964/google-takes-another-step-chinese-market-ai-drawing-game-wechat|date=2018-07-19|access-date=2018-08-06|website=南华早报|dead-url=no|archive-date=2018-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180806040057/https://www.scmp.com/tech/china-tech/article/2155964/google-takes-another-step-chinese-market-ai-drawing-game-wechat}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|language=en|url=https://www.abacusnews.com/big-guns/google-launches-wechat-mini-game-china/article/2155867|title=Google launches a WeChat mini game in China|website=Abacus|date=2018-07-19|access-date=2018-08-06|dead-url=no|archive-date=2018-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180806040036/https://www.abacusnews.com/big-guns/google-launches-wechat-mini-game-china/article/2155867}}</ref>。

2018年8月1日，泄露出来的文件显示，谷歌打算在中国大陆启动审查版的搜索引擎，项目代号是[[蜻蜓计划|Dragonfly]]（蜻蜓）<ref>[https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/topic/detail/205599/ Google為中國推另類版搜尋引擎 搜尋結果會過濾敏感字句] {{Wayback|url=https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/topic/detail/205599/ |date=20180815131541 }}，港生活，2018-08-04</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://theintercept.com/2018/08/01/google-china-search-engine-censorship/|title=GOOGLE PLANS TO LAUNCH CENSORED SEARCH ENGINE IN CHINA, LEAKED DOCUMENTS REVEAL|publisher=The Intercept|date=2018-08-01|accessdate=2018-08-01|language=en-US|author=Ryan Gallagher|dead-url=no|archive-date=2018-08-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180801120009/https://theintercept.com/2018/08/01/google-china-search-engine-censorship/}}</ref>。12月，谷歌公司在內外壓力下放弃研究蜻蜓项目<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.voachinese.com/a/4704437.html |title=有媒体称谷歌放弃迁就中国审查的项目，谷歌未否认 |accessdate=2019-02-18 |archive-date=2019-04-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190404031719/https://www.voachinese.com/a/4704437.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2019年秋季，Google关闭了中国版[[Google地图|Google地图]]<ref>{{cite web | title = Google 疑似关闭了 Google 地图的中国镜像站 | url = https://www.solidot.org/story?sid=62653 | date = 2019-11-19 | website = Solidot | accessdate = 2020-12-11 | archive-date = 2019-11-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191120155636/https://www.solidot.org/story?sid=62653 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，将原页面改为指向Google地图[[Google香港|香港站]]的链接（maps.google.com.hk/maps?hl=zh-CN&sourceid=cnhp）<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://ditu.google.cn/ |title=maps.google.com.hk 请收藏我们的网址 |accessdate=2021-02-06 |archive-date=2021-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210202130534/http://ditu.google.cn/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

